text: Sidi Mohamed Ould Bidjel (born 1 January 1982), is a Mauritanian athlete. Bidjel competed in the 1500 metres at the 2000 Summer Olympics, he finished 14th in his heat so didn't qualify for the next round. ==References== Category:1982 births Category:Living people Category:Olympic athletes of Mauritania Category:Mauritanian male middle-distance runners Category:Athletes (track and field) at the 2000 Summer Olympics
